snippet.title: Wild Country | Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam today!  ➡️  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1515000/Wild_Country/

Wild Country is a cozy-competitive card game with city-building elements! Collect cards, construct buildings, explore Big Sky County, and challenge friends in this cozy competitive strategy game.

Coming to Steam & Nintendo Switch in 2024
